  "detailed_description": "Tall Order is a fastpaced VR game, well suited for social play in the living room.<br><br>Features a number of levels, each with their unique theme:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Feel the rush of climbing in dizzying heights.<br></li><li>Experience the thrill of swinging with grapplehooks, like spiderman.<br></li><li>Plus more to come..</li></ul><br>Local asymmetric gameplay, with one player in VR and the other at the mouse/keyboard:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play against each other. One in VR and the other on the PC.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Tall Order is a fastpaced VR game, well suited for social play in the living room.<br><br>Features a number of levels, each with their unique theme:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Feel the rush of climbing in dizzying heights.<br></li><li>Experience the thrill of swinging with grapplehooks, like spiderman.<br></li><li>Plus more to come..</li></ul><br>Local asymmetric gameplay, with one player in VR and the other at the mouse/keyboard:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play against each other. One in VR and the other on the PC.</li></ul>",
